title: 12/01: Weekend Recap - Mostert, Parker, Barber and More (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Who helped you get into the Fantasy playoffs? We go over the Best of Week 13 (4:00) including Ryan Fitzpatrick, Aaron Rodgers, DeVante Parker, Raheem Mostert, Peyton Barber, Tyler Higbee and Jack Doyle. Plus news and notes (14:30) and an early look at the Waiver Wire (18:15). Can you still get Benny Snell? Darwin Thompson? ... Winners (22:24) like Tyler Boyd and Losers (26:40) like Tevin Coleman and Jonathan Williams. Plus a look at the MegaDuds (32:25)! Sam Darnold, Aaron Jones, Emmanuel Sanders, D.J. Chark and more ... Recapping each game with a "Believe it or Not" from Heath (41:55) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
